---
import balconiesImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/InvisibleGrillforBalconies.png?url';
import windowsImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/InvisibleGrillForWindows.png?url';
import apartmentsImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/InvisibleGrillForApartments.png?url';
import phoneIcon from '../../../assets/Icons/HomeIcons/SmartSaftySolutionsIcons/phonecall.png?url';
---

<section class="third-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h2>Smart Safety Solutions<br>for Every Space</h2>
            <p>From balconies and windows to full apartment protection, our invisible grill systems are designed to deliver safety without disturbing the beauty of your view.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <span class="fast-selling">Fast selling</span>
                    <img src={balconiesImg} alt="Invisible Grill for Balconies" />
                    <button class="call-btn">
                        <img src={phoneIcon} alt="Call" />
                    </button>
                </div>
                <h3>Invisible Grill for Balconies</h3>
                <p>Invisible grills for balconies offer a safe, modern solution with clear views. Made from durable, rust-resistant materials, they provide maximum security without compromising aesthetics.</p>
                <button class="enquiry-btn">Enquiry Now →</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src={windowsImg} alt="Invisible Grill for Windows" />
                    <button class="call-btn">
                        <img src={phoneIcon} alt="Call" />
                    </button>
                </div>
                <h3>Invisible Grill for Windows</h3>
                <p>Invisible grills for windows offer enhanced safety without compromising aesthetics. These sleek, durable grills prevent accidents, providing protection for children and pets.</p>
                <button class="enquiry-btn">Enquiry Now →</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <span class="fast-selling">Fast selling</span>
                    <img src={apartmentsImg} alt="Invisible Grill for Apartments" />
                 <button class="call-btn">
                        <img src={phoneIcon} alt="Call" />
                    </button>   
                </div>
                <h3>Invisible Grill for Apartments</h3>
                <p>Invisible grills for apartments offer enhanced safety by preventing falls without compromising the view. They are sleek, durable, and ideal for balconies, providing secure protection for children and pets.</p>
                <button class="enquiry-btn">Enquiry Now →</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .third-section {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 80px 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 1200px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .header-content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 60px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .header-content h2 {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .header-content p {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .services-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .service-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .card-image {
        position: relative;
        height: 350px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .fast-selling {
        position: absolute;
        top: 16px;
        left: 16px;
        background: #ff6b6b;
        color: white;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .call-btn {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 16px;
        right: 16px;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #B37A42;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .call-btn img {
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
        margin: 20px 20px 12px 20px;
    }

    .service-card p {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #666;
        margin: 0 20px 20px 20px;
    }

    .service-card .enquiry-btn {
        width: calc(100% - 40px);
        margin: 0 20px 20px 20px;
        background: #B37A42;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card .enquiry-btn:hover {
        background: #9a6635;
    }
</style>


